Start a long-running service (localnet, validator, faucet, scoring)

Usage: soma start <COMMAND>

Commands:
  localnet   Start a local SOMA network for development and testing
  validator  Start a validator node from a config file
  faucet     Start a standalone faucet gRPC server
  scoring    Start the scoring service for computing embeddings and distances
  help       Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -h, --help  Print help

EXAMPLES:
    soma start localnet --force-regenesis --small-model
    soma start validator --config validator.yaml
    soma start faucet --port 9123
    soma start scoring --port 9124
